{"tid":2146815,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[已FC]法國仲係好多人唔知...其實BBC個煮飯方法根本冇問題...","createTime":"2020-08-08T21:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T17:23:53.000Z","uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4119462dca1bc916617c77d7a3c82d56f0dc8441","tid":2146815,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:40:57.000Z","msg":"其實當初篇新聞有講到<br />\n<blockquote>有網友找出了影片中的白米包裝，包裝上的確是這樣標示烹飪方式的。另外，似乎歐洲國家的人都是這樣煮飯。所以，影片示範的應該就是歐洲那邊的烹飪方式。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見呢排網上仲有人嘈呢單野<br />\n都已經有唔少報導有講過點解會咁煮,<br />\n不過bbc個主持出黎9UP話自己跟食譜煮都唔澄清自己冇錯...<br />\n其實印度米真係好似BBC咁煮...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWArcqFI9ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaWArcqFI9ag&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=af83d136\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWArcqFI9ag</a><br />\n大家應該要有fc精神,唔好覺得華人咁煮飯就一定啱<br />\n一碌鳩就車埋去評擊人地絕對係錯...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggfriedrice_67782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Ffood%2Frecipes%2Feggfriedrice_67782&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=f53eb2a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggfriedrice_67782</a><br />\n其實份原食譜都係有寫用basmati印度米<br />\n<br />\n不過原post就話BBC美食頻道示範<span class=\"red\">中式炒飯</span>引眾怒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2125017/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2125017/page/1</a><br />\n其實條原片同食譜都應該冇講係中式炒飯,可能有我睇漏左<br />\n不過個煮飯方法真係唔可以話佢唔啱,最多話佢炒錯飯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KpKPueBqFWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKpKPueBqFWc&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=49bf4a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KpKPueBqFWc</a><br />\n<br />\n全世界都話西方人唔尊重中國文化係到上綱上線<br />\n大家有冇尊重過印度人,<br />\n有冇諗過係印度邊境既大兵睇到大家笑鳩佢地...又駁唔到嘴既感受...<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">你有冇諗過長頸鹿既熱咖啡係落到佢喉嚨個陣已經凍左...</span><br />\n<br />\n冇<br />\n<br />\n因為你只會諗你自己..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qco3inE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqco3inE.gif&h=cb55b652&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db91f91dac7c59c4f5cd54f9cad5f7d6bd6efc21","tid":2146815,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:44:26.000Z","msg":"去過泰國就知人地都有獨家方法，連登仔始終擺脫唔到大中華膠，覺得中式煮法最正宗最好食<br />\n<br />\n中肯咁講，煮嘢食邊有啱定錯，好食咪得，樓主好波"},{"pid":"dd832ada572e0cf2e3f789e137f9456af007c9f1","tid":2146815,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:44:33.000Z","msg":"根本就無問題係香港人未見過大蛇屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add2f6459b25b9e1b9268cc2eecc48fffb5a2306","tid":2146815,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd832ada572e0cf2e3f789e137f9456af007c9f1","tid":2146815,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:44:33.000Z","msg":"根本就無問題係香港人未見過大蛇屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:47:24.000Z","msg":"又唔好咁講...<br />\n你見就算西人個邊啲媒體都係恥笑bbc<br />\n又拍啲咩reaction片話鳩佢地..."},{"pid":"2792fb2302cd6d77b93566f0a60ca764168cf406","tid":2146815,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db91f91dac7c59c4f5cd54f9cad5f7d6bd6efc21","tid":2146815,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:44:26.000Z","msg":"去過泰國就知人地都有獨家方法，連登仔始終擺脫唔到大中華膠，覺得中式煮法最正宗最好食<br />\n<br />\n中肯咁講，煮嘢食邊有啱定錯，好食咪得，樓主好波"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:48:23.000Z","msg":"好似我上面咁講啦,又唔洗特登去標籤香港人<br />\n始終大中華文化入侵得太犀利,全世界都覺得飯只可以中式咁煮..."},{"pid":"024ffb976c0c95cb5709eb294922f73a614fe5cb","tid":2146815,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dd832ada572e0cf2e3f789e137f9456af007c9f1","tid":2146815,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:44:33.000Z","msg":"根本就無問題係香港人未見過大蛇屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"h